      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GLORIA KEEPING (6) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.62 beating Loco Storm. Has a tricky draw to overcome but has the ability and in winning form. Winner at her latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. In great form and can continue her winning ways. BOOM BAM RANGER (7) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his lightning win the start prior, getting around Wentworth Park over 520m in 29.38. Expected to feature on best figures. BLUE FRANKY (4) boasts a strong record this course with five wins and four minors from 11 tries. Placed last time (30.35) at Wentworth Park in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 9 lengths. Can feature with the right run. FOXY BARBELLA (2) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
